{"_path":"/maps/_management/shadow-it/shadow-it","_dir":"shadow-it","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"影子 IT","description":"影子 IT 现象、风险与治理策略","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"子主题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"子主题"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_management/shadow-it/ai-accelerated-shadow-it"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 加速的影子 IT"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"概述"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"概述"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"影子 IT（Shadow IT）是指业务部门在未经 IT 部门正式批准或知情的情况下，自行采购、部署和使用信息技术资源的现象。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"影子 IT 现象"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：在大多数中大型组织里，业务团队对数字化的需求远超 IT 部门的交付能力，导致业务团队自行构建解决方案。历史上表现为 Excel/Sheets + VBA/脚本支撑关键流程，或使用低代码、RPA、iPaaS 拼出业务自动化。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI 加速的影子 IT"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：生成式 AI 和无代码平台正在大幅降低\"非工程师自己搭东西\"的门槛。无代码工作流平台原生支持 AI API，AI coding assistant 让具备基本技术素养的非工程师也能生成简单工具和集成。这轮趋势和当年\"用 Excel/表格驱动关键业务流程\"非常像，但潜在影响面更大。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"治理策略"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：组织需要对这种趋势保持警惕，在\"快速解决问题\"与\"长期稳定和可治理性\"之间做清醒的权衡。建议采取分层管理策略：明确禁区（核心财务、监管强约束数据）、区分灰度区（内部协作流程优化）、给予安全区相对宽松的试验空间。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"子主题","depth":2,"text":"子主题"},{"id":"概述","depth":2,"text":"概述"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_management:shadow-it:shadow-it.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_management/shadow-it/shadow-it.md","_stem":"6.maps/_management/shadow-it/shadow-it","_extension":"md"}